name = "Mayura Taran, Diplomat of the Verdant Boughs, Northern Nimbozu"
kingdom = ExtResource("2_nxyue")
portrait = ExtResource("3_nxyue")
greeting = "Greetings to Your Magnificent Highness,"
signoff = "Yours evermore,

Mayura Taran
Diplomat of the Verdant Boughs, Northern Nimbozu"
summerVersion = "I sincerely hope that you have been finding moments of solace in each day despite these uncertain and frankly, disconcerting times; perhaps this letter may serve as one such respite from your woes. After all, I can be quite diverting. 

As you are well aware, Fallowbrook and Nimbozu have the pleasure of meeting land to land at the Eastern River…it naturally follows that we should aspire to become much closer allies. As for the benefits of such a union, I won’t bore you with squabble over grain and coin—I prefer to trade in secrets, invitations, and applause. Besides, I’ve always been of the mind that a startling dress and a sharp mouth is the best persuasion tactic in any negotiation. Alas, this letter and portrait will have to do for now. 

When you do visit, I am sure you will be enraptured by our cloud kingdom’s splendor. From the Swaying Pools of Nyumbe, heated by natural wells of mana, to the Hall of Gilded Wings, where our storytellers master the art of song, every morning you will wake to debate, dance, and a dawn chorus hundreds of leagues in the sky. 

And, because I don’t want you to think me completely shallow, I will mention that our might is nothing to scoff at. While we may be modest in number, our sharp-taloned soldiers are born and bred in thin air—they know not of exhaustion nor defeat. Should we come together, your people would cease to know invasion—or boredom. And truly, what more is necessary for both our kingdoms to take flight into a future of prosperity?"
